                        <h3><a href="#">Cost Analysis</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>One published study showed that bedside shift report was shown to decrease overtime by nurses.</p></div></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Method of Guideline Validation</a></h3>
                    <p>Peer Review</p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Description of Method of Guideline Validation</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>This Best Evidence Statement (BESt) has been reviewed against quality criteria by two independent reviewers from the Cincinnati Children's Hospital Medical Center (CCHMC) Evidence Collaboration.</p></div></p>

